---
/*
  About section — facts only, no editorial, no guidance counselor story.
  Every fact verified against the credentials table.
*/
---

<section class="section-pad" id="about" style="background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--bg),rgba(8,8,6,1),var(--bg))">
  <div class="section-title">About</div>
  <div class="about-wrap">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>
        Mike Ely earned his IFBB Pro card in 2013 at the NPC Masters Nationals with Hany Rambod in his corner. He is a 2x IFBB Pro Masters World Champion, Olympian, and NPC Judge with over three decades in the sport.
      </p>
      <p>
        He holds a BS in Nutritional Science and an MS in Exercise Science from Bowling Green State University. Since 1996, he has coached athletes across every division — bodybuilding, figure, bikini, physique, and wellness — with over 30 athletes earning their IFBB Pro status under his guidance.
      </p>
      <p>
        His programs are built on real science, refined by decades of competition, and custom to every athlete.
      </p>
      <div class="about-stats">
        <div class="about-stat">
          <div class="about-stat-num">2x</div>
          <div class="about-stat-label">World Champion</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat">
          <div class="about-stat-num">30+</div>
          <div class="about-stat-label">Years Competing</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat">
          <div class="about-stat-num stat-text">Thousands</div>
          <div class="about-stat-label">Athletes Coached</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-media">
      <div class="about-photo">
        <img src="/img/gallery-gym-recent.jpg" alt="IFBB Pro Big Mike Ely" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-wrap {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--mu);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-top: 36px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .about-stat {
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }
  .about-stat:not(:last-child)::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    right: -1px;
    top: 10%;
    bottom: 10%;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, var(--accDeep), transparent);
  }
  .about-stat-num {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    line-height: 1;
    background: var(--goldGrad);
    background-size: 200% 100%;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    animation: shimmer 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .about-stat-num.stat-text {
    font-size: 22px;
    letter-spacing: .06em;
  }
  .about-stat-label {
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--dm);
    font-family: var(--mono);
    letter-spacing: .12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .about-photo {
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--borderS);
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.5), 0 0 60px var(--accS);
  }
  .about-photo::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--accB);
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity .3s;
  }
  .about-photo:hover::after { opacity: 1; }
  .about-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    filter: contrast(1.05) brightness(.95);
    transition: transform .6s ease;
  }
  .about-photo:hover img { transform: scale(1.02); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-stats { gap: 24px; }
    .about-stat { padding: 0 12px; }
    .about-stat-num { font-size: 28px; }
    .about-stat-num.stat-text { font-size: 16px; }
    .about-stat:not(:last-child)::after { display: none; }
    .about-stat {
      position: relative;
    }
    .about-stat::before {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 40px;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accDeep), transparent);
      margin: 0 auto;
      position: absolute;
      top: -8px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .about-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr; gap: 60px; }
  }
</style>
